title: Total number of employees of Kohl 's 2012 to 2018
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of employees in thousands, with a total of 7 data points. The chart has 3 significant trends.
The longest trend is slightly negative which exists from 2018 to 2015.
Contrarily, the next significant trend is moderately neutral which exists from 2014 to 2012.
Contrarily, the next significant trend is extremely positive which exists from 2015 to 2014.
gold: This timeline depicts the total number of employees of the Kohl 's Corporation from 2012 to 2018 . In 2018 , the Kohl 's Corporation employed 129,000 associates .
